    "They note that, \"given a U.S. Code citation, GPT-3 can recite plausible but incorrect statutory language\" (Blair-Stanek et al. 2023).",
    "As discussed above, the use of LLMs might be particularly useful to lawyers in the cryptocurrency securities context due to documented resource limitations faced by enforcement attorneys in this area of law.",
    "We use examples from this domain to perform our study.",
    "In this section, we provide a brief outline of the legal context for cryptocurrency securities violations.",
    "A security is \"an investment of money in a commercial, financial, or other business enterprise, with the expectation of profit or other gain produced by the efforts of others\" (Ninth Circuit Jury Instructions Committee 2023)."
